data.description: Located in the sought-after Quail Ridge Suntree neighborhood, steps from the community pool this spacious, well maintained home has 3 large bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with a flex room off the living room and dining room. The kitchen has granite countertops and is open to the living space. A screened in courtyard perfect for enjoying the Florida weather and entertaining. 2 car garage for all your vehicles and toys.
